#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/20.users/index.mdx:21
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "In the portal, users can also click on the avatar in the top-left to configure some other settings such as their identify, mail aliases, automatic mail forwards, or change their password.\n"
